fields.description:
This may be related to the Git polling bug in 1.1, which we're also experiencing. After restarting Hudson today, it started building every job every time it polled SCM. The SCM poll log shows:

{noformat}
Workspace is offline.
Scheduling a new build to get a workspace.
{noformat}

I suspect this is a bad interaction with my slaves being set to on-demand. I filed JENKINS-7641 earlier today, then switched my slave to launch on-demand, since this mitigates the effect of that bug. After that, Hudson started building every job over and over again.
